stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idle : wanted = IDLE
    [*] --> Standby : wanted = PASSIVE [in alliance zone]
    [*] --> Waiting : wanted = PASSIVE [not in alliance zone]
    [*] --> ShooterUnjamming : wanted = REVERSING

    [*] --> PreparingToFire : wanted = SHOOTING or FORCED_SHOT

    PreparingToFire --> Aimed : flywheel + hood + drive ready
    Aimed --> Firing : target ready
    Firing --> Disturbed : hood or drive misaligned
    Disturbed --> Firing : re-aligned within timeout
    Disturbed --> PreparingToFire : disturbance timed out
    Firing --> PreparingToFire : flywheel UNDER_SHOOTING

    note right of Idle
        Flywheel: IDLE
        Hood: IDLE
        Kicker: IDLE
    end note

    note right of Standby
        Flywheel: COASTING
        Hood: DUCKED
        Kicker: IDLE
    end note

    note right of Waiting
        Flywheel: IDLE
        Hood: DUCKED
        Kicker: IDLE
    end note

    note right of PreparingToFire
        Flywheel: SHOOTING
        Hood: AIMING
        Kicker: KICKING [non-WoodBot]
    end note

    note right of Firing
        Flywheel: SHOOTING
        Hood: AIMING
        Kicker: KICKING
        Indexer + Hopper activated
    end note

    note right of Disturbed
        Stays in FIRING mode.
        Tolerates brief misalignment.
        Times out after 0.5s.
    end note
